    <id>http://lition.online/2021/11/13/MCWeibo%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3/</id>
    <published>2021-11-13T09:38:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-11-13T10:11:18.146Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h1><p>MCWeibo是一个在线的微博平台，后端基于Nodejs搭建</p><p>可以通过HTTP请求来发布、获取文章</p><h1 id="api"><a href="#api" class="headerlink" title="api"></a>api</h1><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">[POST] &#x2F;api&#x2F;publish&#x2F;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>用于发布文章</p><p>POST数据示例</p><pre class="line-numbers language-json" data-language="json"><code class="language-json"><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>    <span class="token property">"key"</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">"&#123;key&#125;"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token property">"title"</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">"文章标题"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token property">"subtitle"</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">"文章副标题"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token property">"author"</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">"作者"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token property">"text"</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">"正文"</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">[GET] &#x2F;api&#x2F;page&#x2F;?page&#x3D;&#123;page&#125;&amp;key&#x3D;&#123;key&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>用于通过页码获取页面内容</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">[GET] &#x2F;api&#x2F;essay&#x2F;?id&#x3D;&#123;id&#125;&amp;key&#x3D;&#123;key&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>用于通过id获取具体文章</p><table><thead><tr><th>HTTP状态码</th><th>含义</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>200</td><td>接口正常</td></tr><tr><td>404</td><td>请求的资源未找到</td></tr><tr><td>401</td><td>请求进行身份认证</td></tr><tr><td>416</td><td>请求的范围无效</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
